      • MOVE_SAME_FILES_TO_SAME_LOCATION_TC

        public void MOVE_SAME_FILES_TO_SAME_LOCATION_TC()
        Summary
        Move files to same location
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        Steps
        1. Check if files are available of root location or not
        2. If files are not available to root location than upload the files.
        3. Select files
        4. Click on MoveTo button in ToolBar
        5. Select the location where those files are already exist
        6. click on OK button
        7. Clikc on Process All
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify Files should be Moved to another location

      • MOVE_SAME_FOLDER_TO_SAME_LOCATION_TC

        public void MOVE_SAME_FOLDER_TO_SAME_LOCATION_TC()
        Summary
        Move folder to same location
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        Steps
        1. Verify if the folder is available on root location or not
        2. if folder is not available on root then copy it from the location where is previously moved
        3. Select recently copied folder
        4. Click on MoveTo button in ToolBar
        5. Select location where that folder is already exist
        6. click on OK
        7. Click on Process all button
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify folder should be Moved to another location
